iv class=\"container bread-content\">\r\n<div class=\"breadcrumb\">\r\n<a href=\"/index.htm\">トップ</a><a href=\"/info/recall/index.htm\">リコール等情報</a><a href=\"/info/recall/index.htm\">重要なお知らせ</a>エアバッグリコールに関する大切なお知らせ\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- パンくずナビ -->\r\n<div class=\"section color-f6f7f7\">\r\n<div class=\"wrap\">\r\n<div class=\"container cl-f6f7f7\">\r\n<div class=\"lineup_index\">\r\n<p class=\"big_title\">重要なお知らせ</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- タイトル -->\r\n<div class=\"section\">\r\n<div class=\"wrap\">\r\n<div class=\"container tab-content\">\r\n\r\n<div class=\"recall\">\r\n<div class=\"recall-entry\">\r\n<h3>エアバッグリコールに関する大切なお知らせ</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"recall-article\">\r\n<div class=\"caption\">\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000; font-family: 'Noto Sans Japanese', sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 200; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;\">ダイハツ車をご愛用の皆様には大変ご迷惑をおかけしましたことを心からお詫び申し上げます。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000; font-family: 'Noto Sans Japanese', sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 200; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;\">タカタ製エアバッグのリコールが未実施の場合、</span>車検が更新されません。</p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p>＜対象車種＞</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000; font-family: 'Noto Sans Japanese', sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 200; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;\">対象のお客様にはこれまでに数回ダイレクトメール等で</span>リコールのご案内をさせていただいておりますが、</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000; font-family: 'Noto Sans Japanese', sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 200; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;\">「ミラ」「エッセ」「ハイゼット（トラック除く）」</span><span class=\"txt-red\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: #ffffff; color: #000000; font-family: 'Noto Sans Japanese', sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 200; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">「ハイゼットデッキバン」</span><span style=\"color: #000000; font-family: 'Noto Sans Japanese', sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 200; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;\">が対象です。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000; font-family: 'Noto Sans Japanese', sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 200; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; display: inline !important; float: none;\"><a href=\"https://www.daihatsu.co.jp/info/recall/search/recall_search.php\" title=\"　◆対象車両かどうかを検索する\">　<span style=\"text-decoration: underline; font-size: 14px;\">◆対象車両かの確認はこちらから</span></a></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000; font-family: 'Noto Sans Japanese', sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 200; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;\"></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000; font-family: 'Noto Sans Japanese', sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 200; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: 